1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,490
If the answer is no, back off.

2
00:00:01,600 --> 00:00:03,650
If yes, press ahead.

3
00:00:04,240 --> 00:00:08,529
It's clear we do not make one big jump to success.

4
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:10,850
We get there one step at a time.

5
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:15,250
An excellent plan is to set monthly quotas for accomplishment.

6
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:19,090
Here is a guide to help achieve these goals.

7
00:00:19,360 --> 00:00:20,850
Examine yourself.

8
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:25,490
Decide what specific things you should do to make yourself more effective.

9
00:00:25,759 --> 00:00:31,970
Then, when the 30-day period is up, check your progress and build a new 30-day goal.

10
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:37,009
Always keep working on the little things to get you in shape for the big things.

11
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:41,170
30-Day Improvement Guide.

12
00:00:41,279 --> 00:00:45,650
Between now and the next 30 days, I will... A.

13
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:47,250
Break these habits.

14
00:00:47,360 --> 00:00:48,289
Suggestions.

15
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,090
1.

16
00:00:49,279 --> 00:00:50,610
Putting off things.

17
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:51,410
2.

18
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,930
Negative language.

19
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:53,970
3.

20
00:00:54,160 --> 00:00:57,250
Watching TV more than 60 minutes per day.

21
00:00:57,250 --> 00:00:58,130
4.

22
00:00:58,320 --> 00:00:59,329
Gossip.

23
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:02,450
B. Acquire these habits.

24
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,569
Suggestions.

25
00:01:03,569 --> 00:01:04,370
1.

26
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:07,650
A rigid morning examination of my appearance.

27
00:01:07,650 --> 00:01:08,370
2.

28
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:11,410
Plan each day's work the night before.

29
00:01:11,410 --> 00:01:12,370
3.

30
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:15,890
Compliment people at every possible opportunity.

31
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:21,009
C. Increase my value to my employer in these ways.

32
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,210
Suggestions.

33
00:01:22,210 --> 00:01:23,090
1.

34
00:01:23,279 --> 00:01:26,450
Do a better job of developing my subordinates.

35
00:01:26,450 --> 00:01:27,170
2.

36
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:32,210
Learn more about my company, what it does, and the customers it serves.

37
00:01:32,210 --> 00:01:33,170
3.

38
00:01:33,519 --> 00:01:38,450
Make three specific suggestions to help my company become more efficient.

39
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:43,650
D. Increase my value to my home in these ways.

40
00:01:43,759 --> 00:01:45,730
Suggestions 1.

41
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:51,410
Show more appreciation for the little things my wife does that I've been taking for granted.

42
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:52,210
2.

43
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:56,370
Once each week, do something special with my whole family.

44
00:01:56,370 --> 00:01:57,490
3.

45
00:01:57,680 --> 00:02:02,130
Give one hour each day of my undivided attention to my family.

46
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:05,809
E. Sharpen my mind in these ways.

47
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,930
Suggestions.

48
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:07,730
1.

49
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:13,090
Invest two hours each week in reading professional magazines in my field.

50
00:02:13,090 --> 00:02:13,970
2.

51
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:16,210
Read one self-help book.

52
00:02:16,210 --> 00:02:17,090
3.

53
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,090
Make four new friends.

54
00:02:19,090 --> 00:02:19,970
4.

55
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:24,690
Spend 30 minutes daily in quiet, undisturbed thinking.

56
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:32,529
Next time you see a particularly well-poised, well-groomed, clear-thinking, effective person,

57
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:35,410
remind yourself that he wasn't born that way.

58
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:41,170
Lots of conscious effort, invested day by day, made the person what he is.

59
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:47,970
Building new positive habits and destroying old negative habits is a day-by-day process.

60
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:52,529
Create your first 30-day improvement guide right now.

61
00:02:53,519 --> 00:02:58,610
Often, when I discuss setting goals, someone comments along these lines.

62
00:02:58,960 --> 00:02:59,010
I see that working toward a purpose is important, but so often things happen that upset my plans.
